01:31:36.324 --> 01:31:39.327
"ONE OF THE NATION
OF MANY NATIONS,

01:31:39.327 --> 01:31:40.729
"THE SMALLEST THE SAME...

01:31:40.729 --> 01:31:42.731
"AND THE LARGEST
THE SAME.

01:31:42.731 --> 01:31:44.132
"I DEPART AS AIR.

01:31:44.132 --> 01:31:47.335
"I SHAKE MY WHITE LOCKS
