01:31:49.337 --> 01:31:51.740
"AND DRIFT IT
IN LACY JAGS.

01:31:51.740 --> 01:31:54.342
"I BEQUEATH MYSELF
TO THE DIRT...

01:31:54.342 --> 01:31:57.345
"TO GROW
