01:31:57.345 --> 01:31:59.347
"IF YOU WANT ME AGAIN,

01:31:59.347 --> 01:32:02.150
"LOOK FOR ME
UNDER YOUR BOOT SOLES.

01:32:02.150 --> 01:32:05.754
"YOU WILL HARDLY KNOW
WHO I AM OR WHAT I MEAN,

01:32:05.754 --> 01:32:09.357
"BUT I SHALL BE
GOOD HEALTH TO YOU,
NEVERTHELESS,

01:32:09.357 --> 01:32:12.294
"AND FILTER
AND FIBER YOUR BLOOD.

01:32:12.294 --> 01:32:16.765
"FAILING TO FETCH ME
AT FIRST, KEEP ENCOURAGED.

01:32:16.765 --> 01:32:20.368
"MISSING ME ONE PLACE,
SEARCH ANOTHER.

01:32:20.368 --> 01:32:23.238
